OL,5,FLocal Pollen Information for Scotland
OL,6,Fand North West England
OL,8,FScotland and North West England
OL,9,Fexperience distinct pollen seasons
OL,10,Finfluenced by their respective
OL,11,Fclimates and geographies.
OL,13,FScotland generally experiences
OL,14,Fmoderate grass pollen seasons with
OL,15,Frelatively few high-count days. The
OL,16,Fgrowing seasons are shorter, leading
OL,17,Fto shorter pollen seasons overall.
OL,18,FFrequent rainfall, particularly in the
OL,19,Fwest, often reduces pollen counts to
OL,20,Flow on many days.
