OL,5,FNorth West England
OL,7,FIn North West England, the grass
OL,8,Fpollen season often starts earlier and
OL,9,Flasts longer than in the northeast.
OL,10,FHowever, the seasons are typically
OL,11,Fmilder compared to the Midlands and
OL,12,Fsouthern regions of the UK.
